":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求鳩其開個 炒股炒樓分享會 都屌打運動會決賽啦<br />\n<br />\n根本香港人就只係鍾意炒炒賣賣 ,  肉撚酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人連做運動都只會諗點樣靠運動賺錢<br />\n例如賣產品 賣course 賣運動飲品 搵運動員拍廣告<br />\n<br />\n根本所有野放落香港到都只會變成炒賣工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1633c1ca3b54fb8fbdb0907c5ce42b8cc3d1d5eb","tid":222920,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心冇聽講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記憶之中得巴士電視有廣告</blockquote><br />\n啲街燈有旗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是但搵啲名星、出名運動員，再搵共報共台報都得啦<br />\n但就係無做，擺明唔理，吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7fec5dc14d81e9c6d80a1e66863e5c7d7d0bff","tid":222920,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"香港人做閪運動咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84295a3cc7531296bbc2f3981202b26ee7adefa1","tid":222920,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人做閪運動咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人跑步"},{"pid":"6bbdff6717b81b3b651d1e879d671d770ae2ca73","tid":222920,"uid":101968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人做閪運動咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無落過田徑場？"},{"pid":"76dea833518ef9c3deba8112ae0de08030d60604","tid":222920,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9a38c22af638f3630af7ca9cc55d0aa68177bff","tid":222920,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike